Encrypt
    Insert a string to encrypt

    Step 1: Polybe Array
        Create the Polybe Array
            Generate all combinations "AA", "AD", ..., "VX", "XX"
            
        Complete the array with the specific alphabet
        Convert string to preciphered text

    Step 2 : Permutation
        Create the Key based Array
        Complete the array with the preciphered text
        Permute column according to the alphabetical order of the key
    Get the ciphered text.

